    <entry>
      <title>群晖Docker容器&quot;failed to initialize logging driver database is locked&quot;解决办法</title>
      <link href="/2025/07/09/%E7%BE%A4%E6%99%96failed%20to%20initialize%20logging%20driver%20database%20is%20locked%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%20/"/>
      <url>/2025/07/09/%E7%BE%A4%E6%99%96failed%20to%20initialize%20logging%20driver%20database%20is%20locked%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%20/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>今天docker容器clash出现“failed to initialize logging driver database is locked“错误，查了一下，删除log.db文件即可，</p><span id="more"></span><p>操作如下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo -i</span><br><span class="line"># 切换到root</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">docker ps -a</span><br><span class="line"># 查找出问题容器的ID</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">docker inspect --format=&#x27;&#123;&#123;.LogPath&#125;&#125;&#x27; &lt;容器ID&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 列出容器日志的路径</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">rm &lt;返回日志路径&gt;</span><br><span class="line"># 删除路径下的log.db日志</span><br><span class="line">#重启容器即可</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 技术 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> docker </tag>
            
            <tag> 群晖 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Blurbird的Flexget配置写法</title>
      <link href="/2023/05/25/Blurbird%E7%9A%84Flexget%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>/2023/05/25/Blurbird%E7%9A%84Flexget%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>菜佬提供的配置，还没验证过，因为长时间不登陆，号已经扬了…有兴趣的可以尝试一下</p><span id="more"></span><figure class="highlight yml"><figcaption><span>Flexget.yml</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">bluebird:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">rss:</span> <span class="string">https://bluebird-hd.org/rss.php</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">urlrewrite:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">sitename:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">regexp:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;https://bluebird-hd.org/details.php\?id=(?P&lt;id&gt;\d+)&amp;hit=1&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">format:</span> <span class="string">https://bluebird-hd.org/download.php?id=\g&lt;id&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">headers:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">Cookie:</span> <span class="string">&#x27; 这里写你的 cookies &#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">seen:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">fields:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">url</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">accept_all:</span> <span class="literal">yes</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">template:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">de</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">deluge:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">label:</span> <span class="string">bluebird</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
