    <entry>
      <title>thelounge 安装教程</title>
      <link href="/2022/05/01/thelounge-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>/2022/05/01/thelounge-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://images4.imagebam.com/2f/d3/28/MEPK20G_o.png" alt="图片"><br>thelounge是一个全平台的IRC客户端，下面是在linux下通过的Docker的方式安装：</p><span id="more"></span><p>首先vps上先安装docker：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bash &lt;(curl -sSL https://gitee.com/SuperManito/LinuxMirrors/raw/main/DockerInstallation.sh)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>按提示进行<br><img src="https://images4.imagebam.com/b9/13/6c/MEPK217_o.png" alt="图片"><br><img src="https://images4.imagebam.com/2f/9c/17/MEPK22S_o.png" alt="图片"><br>docker安装完成后，手动创建容器:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ docker run --detach \</span><br><span class="line">--name thelounge \</span><br><span class="line">--publish 9000:9000 \</span><br><span class="line">--volume ~/.thelounge:/var/opt/thelounge \</span><br><span class="line">--restart always \</span><br><span class="line">thelounge/thelounge:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://images4.imagebam.com/28/c8/0f/MEPK237_o.png" alt="图片"><br>刚安装完是默认没有用户的，所以需要创建一个用户。进入容器内创建账户</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker exec -it thelounge /bin/sh</span><br><span class="line"># 进入容器内部</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">thelounge add test</span><br><span class="line"># 按照提示输入密码并回车</span><br><span class="line"># 之后提示是否保存 log 到命令行，默认 yes ，直接回车即可。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 如果未来忘记用户 test 的密码，执行以下命令并根据提示操作：</span><br><span class="line">thelounge reset test</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 如果未来想改用户 test 的密码，执行以下命令并根据提示操作：</span><br><span class="line">thelounge remove test</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://images4.imagebam.com/df/30/3f/MEPK23N_o.png" alt="图片"><br>到此命令行安装过程结束，浏览器打开网址：</p><p><a href="http://localhost:9000/">http://localhost:9000</a></p><p>登录进去打开后，点击左下角齿轮标志进入设置，勾选第一行 Advanced settings 以展开所有设置<br><img src="https://images4.imagebam.com/c1/41/a7/MEPK240_o.png" alt="图片"><br><img src="https://images4.imagebam.com/4c/2c/b1/MEPK2D6_o.png" alt="图片"><br>设置项是即时生效的，无需保存。</p><p>站点设置</p><p>具体设置看图：<br><img src="https://images4.imagebam.com/b3/ef/c2/MEPK2EV_o.png" alt="图片"></p><p>参考资料:<br><a href="https://mylovesaber.gitee.io/pthelp/2020/irc-enhanced/">https://mylovesaber.gitee.io/pthelp/2020/irc-enhanced/</a><br><a href="https://hub.docker.com/r/thelounge/thelounge/">https://hub.docker.com/r/thelounge/thelounge/</a><br><a href="https://hub.docker.com/r/linuxserver/thelounge/">https://hub.docker.com/r/linuxserver/thelounge/</a><br><a href="https://hostloc.com/thread-1010038-1-1.html">https://hostloc.com/thread-1010038-1-1.html</a><br><a href="https://pterclub.com/forums.php?action=viewtopic&forumid=25&topicid=5834">https://pterclub.com/forums.php?action=viewtopic&amp;forumid=25&amp;topicid=5834</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
