    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>nzbget的安装使用</title>
      <link href="/2021/09/27/nzbget%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/"/>
      <url>/2021/09/27/nzbget%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://images4.imagebam.com/21/0c/7c/MEPK1RP_o.png" alt="图片"><br>nzbget，Usenet新闻组的下载工具，需配合provider服务商，推荐newshosting、EWEKA、ninja这三家</p><span id="more"></span><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># wget https://nzbget.net/download/nzbget-latest-bin-linux.run</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">wget https://nzbget.com/download/nzbget-latest-bin-linux.run</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 已经更新，旧版停止维护</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sh nzbget-latest-bin-linux.run</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cd nzbget &amp;&amp; ./nzbget -D</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">登录地址：http://ip-address-of-linux-machine:6789</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">默认用户名:nzbget</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">密码:tegbzn6789</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#SECURITY那边修改用户名和密码</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#如遇到打不开页面</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cd nzbget</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">./nzbget -D</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装完成后，先修改web页面登录的用户名与密码<br><img src="https://images4.imagebam.com/72/34/31/MEPK1UK_o.png" alt="图片"><br>再配置服务商的信息<br><img src="https://images4.imagebam.com/22/1b/b5/MEPK1UT_o.png" alt="图片"><br>设置最大连接数（购买的服务商信息内会提供）<br>OK，可以愉快的玩耍了</p>]]></content>
      
      
